Key Match Events: Myziane Maolida scored the winning goal for Comoros in the 43rd minute.
Comoros held on to a 1-0 win despite Ghana's efforts to equalize.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Comoros secured the top spot in Group I with six points after the win.
Ghana suffered their second consecutive loss to Comoros after a 2021 Afcon 3-2 defeat.
